A = (a_{ij})∈K^{n×n}\ 
a_{ij}=\left\{\begin{array}{cl} 1, & \mbox{if }j =i +1\\ 0, & \mbox{if }j≠ i + 1  \end{array}\right.
k∈ℕ
A^k=A×A×\cdots×A
